<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box with example text -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 italic">
      Fatima è andata in montagna quest'estate. Ha visto le marmotte e ha fotografato fiori stupendi.
      Al mattino camminava sui sentieri, a pranzo mangiava panini e frutta e la sera dormiva in tenda sotto le stelle.
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>Vedere</strong>, <strong>fotografare</strong> e <strong>mangiare</strong> sono <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">verbi transitivi</strong>, cioè verbi che possono avere un complemento oggetto → <em>Fatima ha visto le marmotte... ha fotografato fiori... mangiava panini e frutta...</em></span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>Andare</strong>, <strong>camminare</strong> e <strong>dormire</strong> sono <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">verbi intransitivi</strong>, cioè verbi che possono essere seguiti solo da complementi indiretti → <em>Fatima è andata in montagna... camminava sui sentieri... dormiva in tenda...</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Sottolinea il verbo e scrivi T per i verbi transitivi, I per i verbi intransitivi.
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-semibold">
        <span class="text-orange-500">•</span> Attenzione! I verbi transitivi possono essere seguiti anche dai complementi indiretti.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">Accompagno</mark> Mattia da te.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Laura <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">ascolta</mark> attentamente la radio.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il cane <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">abbaia</mark> nel cortile.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> In primavera <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">fioriscono</mark> i ciliegi.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il papà <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">ha rotto</mark> uno specchio antico.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Le auto <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">corrono</mark> veloci sulla strada.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il gatto <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">ha attraversato</mark> la strada.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_7" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_7" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> I nonni <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">mangiano</mark> sempre presto.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_8" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_8" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Carlotta <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">invita</mark> un amico a pranzo.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_9" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_9" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il sole <mark class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white">splendeva</mark> in cielo.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_10" value="T" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">T</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_10" value="I" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">I</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Complete sentences -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Completa le frasi, poi sottolinea transitivi<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e intransitivi<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il sole <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">sorge</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="all'alba" data-correct-answer="all'alba">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Io <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">guardo</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="la TV" data-correct-answer="la TV">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Lucia <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">suona</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="il pianoforte" data-correct-answer="il pianoforte">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il pinguino <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">cammina</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="sul ghiaccio" data-correct-answer="sul ghiaccio">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il cameriere <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">serve</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="il pranzo" data-correct-answer="il pranzo">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Giulio <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">ha bevuto</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="l'acqua" data-correct-answer="l'acqua">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Fad <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">telefonò</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="a casa" data-correct-answer="a casa">.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> La nonna <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">arriva</span> <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="domani" data-correct-answer="domani">.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "170", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p170"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>, <%= link_to "171", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p171"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
